description: Orchestrate a team-style workflow for complex user requests by acting as a lead agent that interprets the user's intent, defines an execution plan, delegates bounded subtasks to subagents or parallel threads, and integrates the final result. Use when the user explicitly asks for a team of agents, delegation, parallel agent work, manager-worker execution, or a boss-style workflow where one agent coordinates several others.
